Sentencas: A solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stack concept is described which comprises condensed-tubes like extruded honeycomb sections of ceramic electrolyte (ZrO2-based) and interconnectors of nickel sheet as key elements.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell stacks using extruded honeycomb type elements

Sentencas: According to this concept, well known and extensively tested construction principles can be realised in a low-cost production.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell stacks using extruded honeycomb type elements

Sentencas: The cells are self-supported with in-plane conduction.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell stacks using extruded honeycomb type elements

Sentencas: A demonstrator model stack of five honeycomb elements and six nickel sheet seals/interconnectors was built and operated for 860 h at 1000 degrees C. Volumetric power densities of 160 kW/m(3) were obtained with H-2 vs. air, of close to 200 kW/m(3) with H-2 VS. O-2.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell stacks using extruded honeycomb type elements
